videos.headline: Flowers' 21-yard rush gives South Florida the lead
videos.description: South Florida QB Quinton Flowers shows off his elusiveness and rushes 21 yards for the touchdown.

videos.headline: South Florida halts Tulane's drive with INT
videos.description: Tulane QB Jonathan Banks' pass is intercepted by Devin Abraham at the 2-yard line.

videos.headline: Tice gives South Florida their second TD of day
videos.description: South Florida RB Darius Tice breaks loose for a 45-yard touchdown run and gives them a 13-0 lead.

videos.headline: Tulane answers South Florida with long TD
videos.description: Tulane QB Jonathan Banks connects with Terren Encalade for a 73-yard touchdown pass.

videos.headline: South Florida strikes with TD late in half
videos.description: South Florida QB Quinton Flowers hooks up with Darnell Salomon for a 38-yard touchdown pass.

videos.headline: Tice's 43 yard dash moves South Florida in Tulane territory
videos.description: South Florida RB Darius Tice gets the handoff and takes it 43 yards to the Tulane 30-yard line.

videos.headline: South Florida adds to lead with 28-yard TD catch
videos.description: South Florida QB Quinton Flowers tosses up a 28-yard pass to Marquez Valdes-Scantling for the touchdown, giving them a 27-7 lead.

videos.headline: South Florida sets record with latest TD
videos.description: South Florida's D'Ernest Johnson gets the handoff and coasts into the end zone for a 2-yard touchdown. The touchdown puts South Florida over 30 points for the 24th straight game, a record in the AP Poll era.

videos.headline: Tulane gets INT off of deflection from South Florida player's foot
videos.description: South Florida QB Quinton Flowers' pass is intercepted by Donnie Lewis Jr., who catches the deflection and returns it to the Tulane 37-yard line.

videos.headline: Badie breaks tackles on way to Tulane's second TD
videos.description: Tulane RB Sherman Badie breaks multiple tackles on his way to a 36-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Tulane's 24-yard TD cuts South Florida lead
videos.description: Tulane QB Jonathan Banks connects with Dontrell Hilliard for the 24-yard touchdown, cutting the deficit to 34-21.

videos.headline: Tulane blocks FG to keep deficit at 13
videos.description: South Florida kicker Emilio Nadelman has 35-yard field goal blocked by Donnie Lewis Jr.

videos.headline: Hilliard's second TD makes it a one score game
videos.description: Tulane RB Dontrell Hilliard breaks multiple tackles on way to 16-yard touchdown and cutting the South Florida lead to 34-28.

videos.headline: Tice seals win for South Florida with 30-yard rush
videos.description: South Florida RB Darius Tice gets the carry and takes it 30-yards to pick up the first down and cement the win for them.
